        <Stack Gap="3">
            <Heading Level="3" Size="sm" Class="font-semibold">Added</Heading>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground">
                <li><strong>AudioPlayer.</strong> Themed audio player with play/pause, scrub bar, time, volume, optional cover slot, and download button. Wraps the native <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1 text-xs">&lt;audio&gt;</code> element; exposes <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1 text-xs">OnPlay</code> / <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1 text-xs">OnPause</code> / <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1 text-xs">OnEnded</code> / <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1 text-xs">OnTimeUpdate</code> callbacks.</li>
