            <strong>Responsive overlays, polished swipe gesture, and 100% docs parameter coverage.</strong>
            Three threads landed together: a reactive <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-foreground">IResponsiveService</code> + per-overlay mobile overrides so a single <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-foreground">Overlay.ShowSheetAsync</code> can switch from side panel on desktop to fullscreen bottom-sheet on mobile and back across rotation; a swipe gesture rewrite (10px activation deadzone + direction lock + rubber-band) that kills the wackelig feel users reported on small finger movements; and a full sweep of the API tables on every component docs page so every <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-mono text-foreground">[Parameter]</code> is now documented (500+ rows added across 60 pages).
